      <div class="col-12 col-md-4">
        <div class="card-aurora">
          <h3 class="home-gradient-title">See the Big Picture</h3>
          <p class="pb-0 mb-0" style="color: var(--aurora-body); font-size: 0.95rem;">Beyond the ordinary budget tracker, Aurora gives you the bird's eye view of your financial situation using your data. Combine your financial information into one visualization app. Feel empowered to own your future by planning today.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="col-12 col-md-4">
        <div class="card-aurora">
          <h3 class="home-gradient-title">Eliminate Uncertainty</h3>
          <p class="pb-0 mb-0" style="color: var(--aurora-body); font-size: 0.95rem;">No more wondering if you can afford that house, your child's private education, or even your retirement. Know exactly how and when you can make your plans come true. Experience clarity like never before.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="col-12 col-md-4">
        <div class="card-aurora">
          <h3 class="home-gradient-title">Simulate Your Reality</h3>
          <p class="pb-0 mb-0" style="color: var(--aurora-body); font-size: 0.95rem;">Bring your imagination to life by stacking different life events, such as marriage, kids, or career changes to your timeline. Instantly see changes to your financial projections and gain powerful insights to your future.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
